name: Gary Kelly
description: I am single, I don’t drink nor smoke, I generally try to live a healthy lifestyle, exercising and some sort of jogging, 2-3 days a week and eating healthy. I am a grounded, reasonable, hard-working, man, Am positive, funny, thoughtful, generous, wise, gracious, loyal, a good listener & outgoing. I love humor and am a person who tries to only be serious when it’s needed! Life is precious and I believe we have to have a balance in our daily focus.
